Val Halla Golf Course – the ideal location for junior golf development.
Val Halla Golf Course is well known in this region for its commitment to developing junior golfers. Young players will enjoy the dedicated Junior Golf Room and recently constructed putting green. The facility boasts a driving range and two putting greens for a comfortable and safe learning atmosphere for juniors who are just learning as well as those who are developing new skills.
 


