                                                            9am-4pm - Full Day - $350
9am-noon - Half Day - $195                                                        



Aug 21–Aug 25


                                                            9am-4pm - Full Day - $350
9am-noon - Half Day - $195                                                        





Please Note: Camps run Monday through Friday with the exception of the week of July 24-26 which runs Monday through Wednesday.  Full Day Camps are 9am to 4pm, Monday through Thursday and 9am to 12:30pm on Friday.
Camp price does not include a one-time, non-refundable registration fee.
 

